# Comprehensive Gitignore (Whitelist Strategy)

# 1. Ignore Everything by Default
*

# 2. Whitelist Directories (Recursive)
!*/
!cmd/**
!docs/**
!examples/**
!pkg/**
!stdlib/**
!.morph.vz/**
!.vzoel.jules/**

# 3. Whitelist Root Files
!AGENTS.md
!DESIGN.md
!README.md
!ROADMAP.md
!checksum_gen.go
!go.mod
!go.sum
!.gitignore

# 4. Whitelist Github Workflows (if any)
!.github/**

# 5. Explicitly Ignore Artifacts (Just in case they sneak in via whitelist rules)
morph
*.exe
*.o
*.a
*.so
*.dylib
*.test
out.c
